<h2 style="text-align: center;"></h2>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><strong>About our office</strong></h2>
<p>The Housing &amp; Student Living Office works with students to help them make the most of their living situations while attending school here. To do so, we provide both on-campus housing and off-campus support and regulation.</p>
<p><a href="x44817.xml">Student Living</a>&nbsp;provides teaching and support opporunities to help roommates, friends and families strengthen communication and encourage integrity.</p>
<p><a href="x45370.xml">On-Campus Housing</a>&nbsp;is available for both single students and student-families. It provides an inexpensive, close-to-campus option for matriculating students.</p>
<p>Single Student Approved Housing&nbsp;provides a unique opporunity for our office to help ensure students have housing that is physically and spiritually conducive to fulfilling the mission of BYU-Idaho. We provide education, mediation and arbitration services to help resolve issues in Approved Housing.</p>
<p>If you have any questions or concerns about your housing or living situation, please&nbsp;<a class="intLink" href="x45668.xml">contact us</a>&nbsp;and we'd be more than happy to do what we can to help you.</p>]]></BodyCopy><xPower Type="GroupStart" GroupStart="" Name="PageComponents" label="Page Components" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded=""><xPower Type="List" List="xpowercomponent_Optional" Name="OptionalColumnComponent" label="Optional Column Components" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="FacebookComponent;Image;ColumnTextComponent;Media;Quote" Expanded="false"><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="Optional" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="FacebookComponent;Image;ColumnTextComponent;Media;Quote" Expanded="false"/></xPower><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinksColumn1" label="QuickLinks Column 1" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinksColumn2" label="QuickLinks Column 2" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinksColumn3" label="QuickLinks Column 3" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/></xPower><xPower Type="Component" Component="x9764" Name="HighlightedLinks" label="Highlighted Links" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="HighlightedLinksComponent" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Navigation" StartPage="x5" MaxDepth="" MaxNodes="" GenerationOrder="down" Navigation="Ancestors" Query="" Name="AncestorNavigation" label="Ancestor Navigation" readonly="true" hidden="true" required="false" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="x9287" Name="SiteControl" label="Site Control" readonly="true" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="SiteControl" Expanded="false"/></Content>
